data.description: ***Both open houses cancelled this weekend, home is under contract***Welcome to 520 Realm Court. This meticulously maintained townhome embodies the perfect blend of modern updates and inviting comfort. Step inside to discover luxury vinyl plank floors that pave the way into a light-filled dining area, where large windows invite natural light to shine across the space. The layout thoughtfully connects the kitchen to the living room, creating a seamless flow that's ideal for entertaining guests or simply unwinding on cozy evenings. The kitchen serves as the heart of the home, boasting sleek granite countertops, updated appliances, and pristine white cabinetry. A conveniently located powder room on this level adds to the home's functionality. Retreat upstairs to the primary suite, offering a generously sized bedroom, a spacious closet, and a private ensuite bathroom complete with an upgraded quartz vanity. Two additional bedrooms on this floor share access to an updated full bathroom. Venture downstairs to the finished basement, a hidden gem of this home. This versatile area offers endless possibilities, whether you envision it as a cozy family room, a home office, a playroom, or even a home gym. The possibilities are limited only by your imagination, providing ample room to tailor the space to suit your lifestyle and needs. Located in a sought-after neighborhood, this home offers close proximity to popular shopping destinations, diverse dining spots, scenic parks, and major commuter routes, striking a perfect balance between peaceful living and urban convenience. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Schedule a showing today!
